ygData.subject: RE: (OT) Lower level discrimination was Play Time?
ygData.msgSnippet: LOL, no the ship bug was that if you successfully disarmed a ship (removing the anchor perhaps?) the ship would get a big speed boost.  But you would crash
ygData.messageBody:
LOL, no the ship bug was that if you successfully disarmed a ship (removing
the anchor perhaps?) the ship would get a big speed boost. But you would
crash while zoning. So now stop making fun of me or will have to keel-haul
the lot of you :p

Admiral Rokenn
